If we understand that it depends on us how the situation will develop and everyone takes on the corresponding responsibility, not only the leaders, but also every citizen.
Already now I would like to wish everyone a peaceful Christmas and this time also a peaceful New Year's Eve, this time it has to be very peaceful.
And, and we gather strength to be ready for the challenges of next year, because there will be many challenges and not only those related to the corona crisis.
But once again, I believe, I am sure that together we will manage, thank you.
